**Footnote 2:** Scientific Research Records distributed at Box 63, Palm Springs, California for $1.95 plus 25¢ postage

**Footnote 3:** IBM 704 calculation details — three hours of computing, nearly error-free, would have taken ~10,000 man-years with desk calculator

