## References

### Bibliography Structure

- **80 references total** — spans academic papers, newspaper articles, books, government reports, and gambling literature from 1520-1964
- Mix of scholarly publications (**Journal of the American Statistical Association**, **Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences**) and mainstream media (**New York Times**, **Life**, **Sports Illustrated**)
- Heavy concentration of **1960-1964 articles** — media frenzy following publication of Thorp's system

